lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Borna Coric advanced to the Grand Prix Hassan II quarterfinals on Wednesday with a walkover after Italian opponent Simone Bolelli withdrew with a left-knee injury.

headline.print_headline: Coric Advances to Hassan II Quarters Without Hitting a Ball
